7.title: Episode #6.7

8.title: Episode #6.8
8.plot: Tatev tells Felix that Lika and Sevak invited them to a cafe to celebrate the 7th of April. This news upsets Arsen, and he also decides to go to a cafe to "surprise" Lika.

9.title: Episode #6.9
9.plot: When calling Lika from the US, Hrach accidentally learns that his sister dates his old enemy Sevak. Being against the union of Sevak and Lika, Hrach decides to help Arsen in the struggle against Sevak. Sevak finds out that a Lika's ex-boyfriend is a singer named Arsen Grigoryan. He instructs his bodyguards to find all Arsen Grigorians.

10.title: Episode #6.10
10.plot: Sergey brings home a homeless man to make Tamara lose her temper, and insists that he will live with them. Musheg, who came to help, offers a very easy way to get rid of the homeless man, but this leads them to a serious problem.

11.title: Episode #6.11
11.plot: Drunk Sevak behaves indecently at night, by shooting towards Ruben. People from Full house learn about it in the morning and by all means they want to explain to Lika that Sevak is not the angel she fancies, but without a material evidence, they fail to do so. Nevertheless, Arsen and Felix manage to find the man who can unmask Sevak before Lika and uncover the whole truth.

12.title: Episode #6.12
12.plot: Sevak threatens Lika that if she does not continue the relationship with him, he will take drastic measures. Because of Lika's sudden disappearance, everyone thinks that Sevak has abducted her, and are trying to do everything to bring Lika back.

13.title: Episode #6.13

16.title: Episode #6.16
16.plot: Arsen decides to completely ruin the relationship between Lika and Sevak and creates the most unbelievable plan for the implementation of which he needs to make friends with Sevak.

17.title: Episode #6.17

18.title: Episode #6.18

19.title: Episode #6.19

20.title: Episode #6.20
